==Overview==
* [[en/Manual/Main Page]] is an open source project, published under the [http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html GPL]. 
* You can [https://github.com/OpenTTD/OpenTTD view the repository online] and download a copy of the latest source code using [[en/Git]]. 
* The latest changes to the OpenTTD repository can be seen on [https://github.com/OpenTTD/OpenTTD/commits GitHub] ([https://github.com/OpenTTD/OpenTTD/commits/master.atom RSS feed also available!])
* If you modify the source you can submit a [https://github.com/OpenTTD/OpenTTD/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#pull-requests pull request] with your changes to the repository.
*[https://github.com/OpenTTD/OpenTTD/issues Bug tracker]

==Development Docs==
There is no single source for OpenTTD development docs.  It's a complex project with a long history, and multiple APIs.

For developing the core game, the "OpenTTD Development Documentation" sidebar navigation an entry point, with links to development docs on this wiki, and external sources such as our GitHub and Doxygen.

